870
00:46:07,982 --> 00:46:09,916
这是真的吗？
Is that true?

871
00:46:10,084 --> 00:46:13,178
我不知道 不过我一直很喜欢这个故事
I don't know. I always liked the story, though.

872
00:46:13,354 --> 00:46:14,719
没错，很震撼的一个故事
Yeah, that's a great story.

873
00:46:14,956 --> 00:46:17,823
你相信巴黎圣母院有一天会消失吗？
But you have to think that Notre Dame will be gone one day.

